OL,3,CAnti-slavery day: 'Global epidemic'
OL,4,Csees 50 million exploited worldwide
OL,6,FThey've been trafficked. They are
OL,7,Fbeing abused as modern day slaves.
OL,9,FI had never heard of the crime.
OL,11,FJuliet is planning to set up a charity
OL,12,Fto support victims of it and is hoping
OL,13,Fto start raising profile around the
OL,14,Fissue.
OL,16,FShe takes me to meet a young woman
OL,17,Fcalled Omosovie (not her real name)
OL,18,Fwho is being held at Holloway prison
OL,19,Fon immigration offences, whom she is
OL,20,Ftrying to support.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
