OL,6,FShe'd been infected with HIV, and he
OL,7,Fhad forbidden her from seeing a
OL,8,Fdoctor. And now she was being treated
OL,9,Fas a criminal rather than as a victim.
OL,11,FIt was a story which has never left
OL,12,Fme, and which I've just recounted in
OL,13,Fan interview with the Anti-Slavery
OL,14,FCollective - an organisation set up by
OL,15,FPrincess Eugenie and her friend Julia
OL,16,Fde Boinville.
