OL,3,CAnti-slavery day: 'Global epidemic'
OL,4,Csees 50 million exploited worldwide
OL,6,FHere are the statistics which never
OL,7,Ffail to shock.
OL,9,FA global epidemic of modern slavery in
OL,10,Fwhich 50 million are being coerced and
OL,11,Fcontrolled by criminals - in forced
OL,12,Flabour, forced marriage. Organ
OL,13,Fharvesting. Drugs running. Child
OL,14,Fsoldiers. Exploited and abused. On and
OL,15,Fon.
OL,17,FSome are tattooed as property of
OL,18,Fgangmasters. These are human barcodes.
OL,20,FTwelve million of that number are
OL,21,Fchildren.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
