OL,3,CAnti-slavery day: 'Global epidemic'
OL,4,Csees 50 million exploited worldwide
OL,6,FIt's happening under our noses in all
OL,7,Four towns and cities. In nail bars, in
OL,8,Fcar washes, in agriculture.
OL,10,FOn Anti-Slavery Day I'm thinking of
OL,11,Fthose who've courageously shared their
OL,12,Fstories.
