OL,3,CAnti-slavery day: 'Global epidemic'
OL,4,Csees 50 million exploited worldwide
OL,6,FThanh, the young Vietnamese woman who
OL,7,Fwas thirty years a slave. Trafficked
OL,8,Fto China at the age of five - used as
OL,9,Fa drugs runner. At puberty, put to sex
OL,10,Fwork. Raped so often she couldn't sit
OL,11,Fcomfortably in the chair for long as
OL,12,Fthe violence had damaged her back.
OL,14,FTrafficked into Russia to work on
OL,15,Ffarms, then into France for more sex
OL,16,Fwork. Brought into Britain in a
OL,17,Frefrigerated lorry to live in a
OL,18,Fbasement in London and sent out to
OL,19,Fpack vegetables.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
