OL,6,FShe only escaped when she got medical
OL,7,Ftreatment for what turned out to be
OL,8,Fbreast cancer. Thankfully, she is now
OL,9,Ffree of her slave masters and
OL,10,Frebuilding her life.
OL,12,FI'm thinking of the Nigerian women who
OL,13,Fhad made the journey through Africa
OL,14,Fwith the hope of a better life in
OL,15,FEurope, only to be enslaved in Libya
OL,16,Ffor sex work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
