OL,6,FWhen they became pregnant and
OL,7,Ftherefore no longer profitable - they
OL,8,Fwere thrown into boats with dozens of
OL,9,Fothers and pushed off to Italy. They
OL,10,Fgathered in Turin with their babies in
OL,11,Fa shelter.
OL,13,FAnd I'm thinking of the 53-year-old
OL,14,Fgrandmother called Susan who was
OL,15,Fcuckooed in her own home in the north
OL,16,Fwest. A drugs gang took over her home
OL,17,Fand forced her to run drugs for them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
