OL,3,CAnti-slavery day: 'Global epidemic'
OL,4,Csees 50 million exploited worldwide
OL,6,FIf someone is selling anything too
OL,7,Fcheaply - is someone being exploited
OL,8,Fbecause of it? Do the women working in
OL,9,Fyour local nail bar look scared of
OL,10,Ftheir boss? Is there a pop up car wash
OL,11,Fwhere it's uncannily cheap and the
OL,12,Fworkers look uncared for? When you're
OL,13,Fbuying clothes online - what do you
OL,14,Fknow or suspect about the supply chain?
OL,16,FI often think of Omosovie.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
