OL,3,CAnti-slavery day: 'Global epidemic'
OL,4,Csees 50 million exploited worldwide
OL,6,FSadly despite all my friend Juliet's
OL,7,Fbest efforts, she eventually fell back
OL,8,Finto the hands of her traffickers, due
OL,9,F- probably - to a greater fear of the
OL,10,Fauthorities back then treating her as
OL,11,Fa criminal.
OL,13,FBut there are many stories of hope
OL,14,Ftoo. Thanh built a new life. The
OL,15,Fawareness of the crime is growing.
OL,17,FThis oldest of affronts to life - the
OL,18,Fenslavement of another human being -
OL,19,Fendlessly need fresh energy,
OL,20,Fcreativity and political pressure to
OL,21,Fcounter it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
